            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 bg-surface border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-5">
            <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
              <li>
                Initiated auth with{" "}
                <code class="font-mono text-sm bg-elevated px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-amber">
                  npx awal auth login tommeredith@supertrained.ai
                </code>
              </li>
              <li>
                Pulled the OTP from Gmail with{" "}
                <code class="font-mono text-sm bg-elevated px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-amber">
                  gog gmail list --from no-reply@info.coinbase.com
                </code>
              </li>
              <li>
                Verified the login with{" "}
                <code class="font-mono text-sm bg-elevated px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-amber">
