          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Total human actions required: zero. Wallet auth is already agent-automatable if the
            agent controls the inbox.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section id="the-human-does-less-than-you-think" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-8">
